d%20through%20the%20cemetery%2C%20and%20we%20ate%20pizza%20at%20her%20house%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20one%20day%20at%20a%20time%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20move%20forward%20and%20how%20to%20support%20her%20besides%20being%20present%20and%20keeping%20her%20company%20in%20the%20silence.%20We%20started%20scheduling%20regular%20visits%3B%20I%20would%20go%20down%20and%20stay%20the%20weekend%20with%20her%2C%20help%20her%20organize%20the%20mail%2C%20drop%20off%20packages%2C%20pick%20up%20groceries%2C%20and%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousehold-chores-changes-history-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehousehold%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20needed%20my%20assistance%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20bond%20really%20deepened%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20so%20much%20about%20my%20grandma%2C%20and%20our%20bond%20as%20her%20oldest%20grandkid%20deepened.%20We%20shared%20inside%20jokes%20about%20Grandpa's%20burial%20experience%2C%20watched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-popular-hallmark-christmas-movies-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHallmark%20movies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20went%20through%20the%20Culver's%20drive-thru%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20inside%20jokes%20went%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20secrets%20we%20would%20share.%20I%20talked%20with%20Grandma%20about%20dating%2C%20being%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fhow-to-start-a-conversation-on-a-dating-app%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20struggles%20of%20trying%20to%20meet%20people%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20explained%20how%20draining%20it%20was%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-date-red-flags-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentify%20people%20with%20red%20flags%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20get%20past%20the%20talking%20stage%2C%20and%20she