0not%20feel%20adequate%20to%20capture%20their%20shared%20lived%20experiences%2C%20even%20though%20it%20made%20her%20smile%20to%20have%20him%20referred%20to%20as%20such.%20We%20settled%20on%20beau%20as%20his%20romantic%20label%2C%20and%20I%20became%20her%20%26quot%3Bofficial%20dating%20coach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrandma's%20new%20beau%20had%20also%20lost%20a%20spouse%20to%20cancer%2C%20and%20she%20frequently%20told%20me%20about%20how%20important%20that%20shared%20lived%20experience%20was%20to%20her.%20Watching%20from%20the%20sidelines%2C%20she%20took%20to%20dating%20much%20more%20easily%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneration-you-are-in-by-birth-year-millennial-gen-x-baby-boomer-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20baby%20boomers%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20in%20her%20situation.%20My%20grandma%20is%20good%20at%20asking%20questions%2C%20giving%20information%2C%20and%20she%20spent%20lots%20of%20time%20analyzing%20her%20new%20beau's%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EShe%20would%20send%20me%20outfit%20checks%20before%20dates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrandma%20would%20send%20me%20outfit%20checks%20before%20a%20date%2C%20asking%20about%20the%20level%20of%20dressiness%20depending%20on%20the%20venue.%20Her%20favorite%20color%20is%20Wisconsin%20Badger%20red%2C%20often%20donning%20a%20blazer%20or%20turtleneck%20sweater%20for%20the%20cooler%20months.%20My%20girlfriend%20and%20I%20would%20offer%20tips%20about%20layering%2C%20accessorizing%2C%20and%20makeup%20tips.%20These%20'fit%20checks%20would%20usually%20come%20early%20Friday%20mornings%20since%20she%20had%20a%20recurring%20appointment%20every%20Friday%20for%20lunch%20with%20her%20new%20beau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20regular%20plans%20became%20a%20highlight%20of%20her%20week%20and%20our%20weekend%20debrief%20when%20I%20came%20to%20visit%2C%20we%20would%20giggle%20and%20share%20pictures%20and%20recount%20the%20events%20over%20ice%20cream%20sundaes%20late%20into%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp