affairs%20at%20the%20National%20Restaurant%20Association%2C%20said%20in%20a%20US%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20press%20call.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20top%20three%20items%3A%20wings%2C%20pizza%2C%20and%20then%20salsa%20dips%20and%20spreads.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20Taylor%20Swift%20of%20it%20all.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20demographic%20is%20tuning%20in%20for%20what%20could%20be%20a%20record-breaking%20number%20of%20viewers.%2021%25%20of%20Americans%20surveyed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shu.edu%2Fbusiness%2Fnews%2Fnumber-planning-to-watch-super-bowl-up-taylor-swift.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESeton%20Hall%20Sports%20Poll%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20yes%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20had%20something%20to%20do%20with%20them%20or%20someone%20in%20their%20household%20deciding%20to%20watch%20the%20game.%20It%20makes%20sense%20that%20spending%20is%20up%20and%20that%20it's%20following%20more%20gendered%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Kennedy%20said%20that%20women%2C%20by%20a%20sprawling%20margin%2C%20view%20chips%20and%20salsa%20as%20Super%20Bowl%20must-haves%20and%20feel%20similarly%20about%20nachos.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20may%20order%20their%20nachos%20from%20restaurants%2C%20others%20will%20make%20them%20at%20home.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20grocery%20inflation%20has%20cooled%20much%20faster%20than%20inflation%20at%20restaurants%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20recently%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20started%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-prices-cheapest-option-groceries-restaurants-fast-food-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebecome%20a%20better%20deal%20to%20make%20food%20at%20home%20than%20order%20out%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20Americans%20may%20still%20be%20opting%20to%20outsource%20their%20Super%20Bowl%20meals%20%E2%80%94%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20restaurant%20industry.%20The%20N