essinsider.com%2Fwhy-germanys-free-college-education-is-actually-not-that-great-2014-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%20for%20free%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Choosing%20to%20pursue%20my%20master's%20degree%20in%20Hamburg%2C%20I%20moved%20there%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20story%20short%2C%20things%20didn't%20work%20out%20as%20planned.%20I%20failed%20the%20mandatory%20language%20test%20to%20get%20into%20the%20university%2C%20lost%20my%20student%20visa%2C%20and%20almost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-germany-from-us-school-almost-deported-dont-regret-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egot%20deported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Still%2C%20moving%20here%20has%20been%20a%20powerful%20financial%20decision%2C%20and%20led%20me%20to%20a%20cherished%20career%20in%20international%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20facing%20immense%20difficulty%20with%20the%20bureaucratic%20systems%20and%20still%20struggling%20to%20fit%20in%2C%20I've%20remained%20in%20Germany%20for%20eight%20years%2C%20here%20are%20the%20main%20reasons%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20The%20German%20social%20support%20system%20actually%20supports%20individuals%20and%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20provides%20no%20federal%20mandate%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-america-doesnt-have-paid-leave-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eparental%20leave%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Germany%20offers%20loads%20of%20support%20for%20starting%20a%20family%20%E2%80%94%20even%20for%20those%20who%20are%20self-employed.%20I%20run%20my%20own%20international%20marketing%20agency%20in%20Germany%2C%20and%20I'm%20still%20entitled%20to%20parental%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Germany%2C%20all%20family-related%20social%20benefits%20are%20outlined%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffamilienportal.de%2Ffamilienportal%2Fmeta%2Flanguages%2Ffamily-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFamily%20Ministry%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20include%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EFamilies%20receive%20up%20to%2012%20months%20of%20paid%20parental%20leave%20(in%20total%20per%20family%2C%20per%20child)%20with%2062%20to%2067%25%20of%20the%20parent's%20last%20net%20salary%2C%20capped%20at%20a%20monthly%20net%20income%20that%20converts%20to%20around%20%241%2C900.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EFamilies%20are%20provided%20a%20minimum%20that%20converts%20to%20about%20%24270%20a%20month%20in%20Kindergeld%20(financial%20aid%20for%20families%20with%20children)%20per%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20your%20parental%20leave%2C%20your%20employer%20legally%20can't%20fire%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20pay%20a%20reduced%20percentage%20of%20income%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20Social%20Security%20contribution%20decreases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20medical%20expenses%20related%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20your%20child%2C%20as%20well%20as%20midwife%20support%20afterward%2C%20are%20covered%20by%20health%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20child%20is%20sick%2C%20you%20are%20allowed%2015%20days%20of%20paid%20leave%20per%20parent%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20EU%20minimum%20annual%20paid%20holidays%20of%2020%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20may%20not%20stay%20in%20Germany%20forever%2C%20we're%20starting%20a%20family%20soon%20in%20order%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20familial%20support%20system%20(which%20we%20deserve%20by%20now%20after%20paying%20so%20much%20into%20the%20tax%20system%20for%20many%20years).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20I've%20established%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20German%20and%20European%20business%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20American%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-shows-hardest-languages-to-learn-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enative%20English%20speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20unique%20expertise%20in%20international%20culture%20and%20my%20ability%20to%20speak%20multiple%20languages%20have%20enabled%20me%20to%20gain%20financial%20success%20in%20Germany.%20The%20international%20marketing%20agency%20I%20founded%20is%20based%20on%20that%20concept%2C%20as%20we%20specialize%20in%20helping%20international%20companies%20expand%20into%20Germany%20and%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20come%20to%20realize%20that%20regardless%20of%20where%20I%20live%2C%20I%20need%20to%20maintain%20a%20deep%20connection%20to%20Germany%2C%20in%20order%20to%20maintain%20my%20career%20path.%20I%20likely%20will%20never%20permanently%20leave%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Traveling%20to%20new%20countries%20doesn't%20take%20ages%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-travel-surprising-things-american-in-europe-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETraveling%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20so%20easy.%20The%20well-connected%20transport%20system%20makes%20exploring%20neighboring%20countries%20and%20even%20the%20UK%20a%20breeze.%20While%20not%20as%20budget-friendly%20as%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fberlin-travel-guide-germany-trip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fa%3E%20travel%20abroad%20every%20few%20months.%20I've%20traveled%20to%2025%20countries%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20because%20of%20how%20well-connected%20the%20flights%20and%20train%20systems%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20go%20home%20to%20visit%20my%20family%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20takes%2030%20hours%20and%20four%20flights%20(they%20live%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%20in%20Oregon)%2C%20but%20most%20destinations%20within%20Europe%20only%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20to%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20I%20don't%20have%20suspicion%20about%20whether%20the%20police%20truly%20want%20to%20help%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20the%20US%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnumber-of-mass-shootingsin-america-this-year-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerns%20about%20gun%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20part%20of%20everyday%20life%2C%20the%20increased%20levels%20of%20safety%20in%20Germany%20have%20been%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air.%20Though%20violent%20crime%20still%20exists%20in%20large%20cities%20(and%20is%20a%20primary%20reason%20we%20plan%20to%20move%20to%20a%20smaller%20city%20soon)%2C%20it's%20incomparable%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhereas%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20often%20feared%20the%20police%20due%20to%20corruption%2C%20shootings%2C%20and%20a%20for-profit%20mindset%2C%20in%20the%20eight%20years%20I've%20lived%20in%20Germany%2C%20I've%20had%20to%20call%20the%20police%20and%20ambulance%20multiple%20times%20for%20various%20reasons%20and%20they've%20always%20been%20incredibly%20helpful%2C%20even%20speaking%20English%20with%20me%20most%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20I've%20fallen%20in%20love%20with%20the%20Turkish%20culture%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-germany-relocation-american-move-disappointing-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIntegrating%20into%20German%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20challenging%20due%20to%20its%20closed-off%20nature%2C%20but%20the%20expat%20community%2C%20particularly%20the%20Turkish%20community%2C%20has%20become%20my%20community%20anchor.%20There's%20a%20massive%20Turkish%20community%20in%20Germany%2C%20both%20expats%20and%20first-generation%20Germans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20married%20to%20a%20Turkish%20man%2C%20who%20I%20met%20while%20living%20in%20Germany.%20I've%20also%20found%20incredible%20support%20within%20%26quot%3BThe%20Turkwerk%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20term%20I%20playfully%20coined%20that%20combines%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BTurkish%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnetwork.%26quot%3B%20It%20describes%20the%20tight-knit%20Turkish%20community%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20come%20together%20and%20help%20one%20another%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20location.%20Their%20emphasis%20on%20family%20and%20kindness%20has%20made%20me%20feel%20accepted%20from%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E6.%20Insurance%20provides%20coverage%2C%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20get%20out%20of%20payments%20with%20vague%20loopholes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Germany%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-healthcare-and-insurance-work-around-the-world-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%20is%20basically%20a%20way%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20live%20here%20long%20enough%2C%20you'll%20end%20up%20having%20insurance%20for%20almost%20everything.%20I've%20always%20been%20on%20private%20health%20insurance%20and%20it%20has%20covered%20all%20expenses%2C%20even%20when%20I%20was%20once%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20where%20I%20rent%20a%20car%2C%20I%20use%20my%20German%20insurance%20because%20it%20has%20absolutely%20stellar%20coverage.%20I%20was%20once%20on%20a%20road%20trip%20in%20South%20Africa%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20our%20tire%20popped%2C%20causing%20us%20to%20total%20the%20car.%20My%20German%20insurance%20covered%20everything%20and%20it%20was%20a%20really%20easy%20process%20to%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsurance-companies-get-you-to-pay-more-deny-claims-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnlike%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20German%20insurance%20companies%20genuinely%20aim%20to%20help%20if%20you've%20set%20up%20the%20correct%20terms%20in%20your%20contract%20%E2%80%94%20provided%20you%20keep%20your%20paperwork%20in%20order.%20If%20there's%20one%20tip%20I%20can%20give%20anyone%20about%20Germany%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20keep%20every%20paper%20from%20everything.%20I%20guarantee%2C%20one%20day%20you'll%20be%20asked%20to%20provide%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E7.%20Germany%20is%20more%20transparent%20about%20the%20ingredients%20in%20the%20food%20we%20buy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20visited%20my%20family%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20seven%20years%20and%20I%20noticed%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20added%20sugar%20and%20preservatives%20in%20so%20many%20foods.%20The%20EU%20and%20Germany's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fknowledge4policy.ec.europa.eu%2Fhealth-promotion-knowledge-gateway%2Fsugars-sweeteners_en%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLabelling%2520of%2520sugars%2520in%2520the%2520EU%2C-In%2520the%2520EU%26amp%3Btext%3DUnder%2520Regulation%2520(EU)%25201924%252F%2C100%2520g%2520or%2520100%2520ml%2527.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estricter%20regulations%20regarding%20hidden%20sugars%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20organic%20labeling%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20transparent%20about%20what's%20actually%20in%20the%20food%20we%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20German%20cuisine%20may%20not%20be%20inherently%20healthy%20(it's%20basically%20constant%20meat%20and%20potatoes)%2C%20the%20main%20ingredients%20contribute%20to%20a%20more%20balanced%20diet%20because%20it's%20less%20processed.%20I%20now%20understand%20why%20my%20friends%20didn't%20really%20like%20it%20when%20I%20cooked%20American-style%20foods.%20We%20use%20so%20much%20more%20sugar%20and%20butter%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E8.%20I'm%20not%20constantly%20bombarded%20with%20TV%20commercials%20for%20antidepressants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%20TV%20commercials%20are%20typically%20filled%20with%20pharma%20ads%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feur-lex.europa.eu%2Flegal-content%2FEN%2FTXT%2F%3Furi%3DLEGISSUM%253Al21143%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGermany%20has%20basically%20banned%20that%20entirely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20last%20visited%20the%20US%20that%20was%20another%20area%20that%20shocked%20me%2C%20as%20I%20remember%20watching%20commercials%20for%20additives%20to%20antidepressants%20that%20also%20helped%20with%20weight%20loss.%20It's%20really%20sad%20to%20see%20because%20it's%20a%20clear%20sign%20of%20the%20immense%20health%20issues%20many%20Americans%20face%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20regulations%20to%20cull%20the%20for-profit%20mind%20of%20Big%20Pharma.%20I'm%20so%20grateful%20for%20the%20EU%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Germany%2C%20the%20pharma%20industry%20is%20heavily%20regulated%20by%20the%20government%20and%20I%20trust%20the%20medications%20doctors%20prescribe%20me%2C%20as%20they're%20not%20incentivized%20by%20commissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20my%20journey%20in%20Germany%20hasn't%20been%20anything%20like%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20a%20new%20family%2C%20established%20a%20successful%20career%2C%20have%20found%20financial%20stability%2C%20and%20have%20far%20less%20fear%20about%20the%20future%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20having%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-from-us-to-germany-better-support-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707473461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c332517a3d27148878682b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-from-us-to-germany-better-support-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20American%20who%20moved%20to%20Germany%20says%20she%20feels%20more%20supported%20living%20there%2C%20from%20the%20country's%20Family%20Ministry%20to%20its%20police%20and%20insurance%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Adriana%20Stein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-from-us-to-germany-better-support-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jungkook%20to%20feature%20in%20Usher%E2%80%99s%20Super%20Bowl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170747323500