You%20also%20no%20longer%20get%20voting%20representation%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%20or%20a%20voice%20in%20presidential%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-san-juan-puerto-rico%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20offer%20visitors%20and%20residents%2C%20with%20its%20beautiful%20beaches%2C%20forests%20filled%20with%20abundant%20wildlife%2C%20a%20generally%20laid-back%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20even%20a%20major%20city%20in%20San%20Juan%20that%20is%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftraveltips.org%2Fsan-juan-vs-miami%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompared%20to%20Miami%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20some%20who%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-puerto-rico-tax-benefits-healthcare-residency-requirements-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20the%20island%20full-time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20can%20come%20with%20some%20pretty%20sweet%20tax%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20Americans%2C%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20easy.%20As%20a%20US%20territory%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20US%20citizen%2C%20the%20door%20is%20open%20for%20you%20to%20live%20there%2C%20as%20it%20would%20be%20in%20any%20American%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investpr.org%2Fwhy-puerto-rico%2Ftax-benefits-policy%2F%3Fnis%3D6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAct%2060%3C%2Fa%3E%20provides%20financial%20incentives%20to%20entice%20Americans%20to%20move%20to%20the%20island%20permanently.%20If%20you%20qualify%20for%20an%20Act%2060%20decree%2C%20it%20includes%20a%204%25%20income%20tax%20rate%2C%20a%2075%25%20discount%20on%20property%20tax%2C%20and%20no%20tax%20on%20capital%20gains%20accrued%20while%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20the%20Act%2060%20benefits%2C%20you%20have%20to%20become%20what%20is%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bbona%20fide%26quot%3B%20resident%2C%20and%20that%20comes%20with%20some%20strict%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Presence%20Test%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20a%20Puerto%20Rican%20resident%20you%20need%20to%20do%20some%20of%20the%20normal%20things%20you%20do%20if%20you%20moved%20to%20other%20states%2C%20such%20as%20register%20to%20vote%20and%20obtain%20a%20local%20driver's%20license.%20However%2C%20for%20the%20tax%20breaks%2C%20there%20is%20an%20added%20layer%20in%20which%20you%20need%20to%20establish%20your%20presence%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20you%20can't%20just%20buy%20a%20house%20on%20the%20island%20and%20claim%20residency%20if%20you%20never%20lived%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frelocatepuertorico.com%2Firs-residency-requirements-for-puerto-rico%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuerto%20Rican%20regulations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20several%20ways%20exist%20to%20establish%20a%20%26quot%3Bpresence%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20island.%20The%20easiest%20is%20to%20show%20that%20you%20were%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20for%20more%20than%20half%20the%20year%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20183%20days%20%E2%80%94%20or%20an%20average%20of%20at%20least%20183%20days%20over%203%20years%2C%20with%20a%20minimum%20of%2060%20days%20in%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Condado%20Beach%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%20skyline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3d2036fcb546d2d4d2674%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECondado%20Beach%20skyline%20in%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3ESean%20Pavone%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20spend%20fewer%20than%20183%20days%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20you%20can%20still%20qualify%20if%20you%20can%20show%20that%20you%20did%20not%20spend%20more%20than%2090%20days%20during%20the%20year%20in%20one%20of%20the%2050%20US%20states%20or%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20occasional%20exceptions%20made%20to%20the%20183-day%20rule.%20For%20example%2C%20in%202017%2C%20after%20Hurricane%20Maria%20devastated%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdsupra.com%2Flegalnews%2Firs-provides-relief-for-bona-fide-91469%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIRS%20gave%20people%20up%20to%20117%20days%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20they%20could%20not%20return%20to%20the%20island%20because%20of%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20'closer%20connection'%20test%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20cannot%20have%20anything%20deemed%20a%20%26quot%3Bcloser%20connection%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20US%20state.%20This%20could%20be%20belongings%20or%20even%20personal%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Flynn%2C%20a%20semi-retired%20IT%20consultant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-puerto-rico-tax-benefits-healthcare-residency-requirements-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Humacao%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20in%202021%20from%20Austin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20did%20not%20move%20to%20the%20island%20for%20the%20tax%20breaks%20but%20that%20they%20certainly%20%26quot%3Bsweetened%20the%20pot.%26quot%3B%20He%20explained%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bcloser%20connection%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20mainland%20can%20be%20vague%20and%20determined%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis%20but%20a%20few%20things%20are%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20could%20be%20like%20a%20residence%20in%20Texas%2C%20and%20I%20stayed%20there%20for%20more%20than%2030%20days%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20that%20could%20be%20considered%20a%20closer%20connection%20to%20the%20mainland%2C%26quot%3B%20Flynn%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20If%20I%20were%20married%20and%20she%20didn't%20claim%20residency%20and%20she%20still%20claimed%20residency%20to%20Texas%2C%20that%20could%20become%20an%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlynn%20noted%20that%20the%20housing%20situation%20can%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20some%20wealthier%20mainlanders%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20who%20want%20to%20keep%20a%20house%20in%20the%20States%20and%20split%20their%20time.%20He%20notes%20this%20could%20violate%20their%20decree%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20if%20they%20visit%20the%20mainland%20too%20much%2C%20and%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20draw%20closer%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20IRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Puerto%20Rico%20children.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3d2c07a3d27148878af32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20tax%20breaks%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20you%20can't%20leave%20your%20children%20back%20on%20the%20mainland.%3Cp%3EMark%20Rubens%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20government%2C%20other%20things%20to%20consider%20are%20where%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20immediate%20family%20lives%2C%20such%20as%20children%2C%20where%20you%20conduct%20your%20business%2C%20where%20your%20primary%20bank%20is%20located%2C%20and%20where%20your%20personal%20belongings%20are%20stored%2C%20including%20cars%2C%20furniture%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20jewelry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20those%20things%20are%20allowed%20to%20be%20in%20the%20mainland%20US%20if%20you%20want%20to%20claim%20%26quot%3Bbona%20fide%26quot%3B%20Puerto%20Rican%20residency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBecoming%20a%20bona%20fide%20resident%20can%20be%20pricey%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20ensure%20that%20the%20people%20enjoying%20the%20tax%20incentives%20of%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20are%20wealthy%20enough%20to%20help%20boost%20the%20local%20economy%2C%20the%20government%20has%20included%20a%20required%20donation%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Act%2060%20decree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3