%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20high%20non-GST%20expenses%20at%20home%2C%20after%20school%20and%20college%20fee%20and%20healthcare%20expenses%2C%20include%20the%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20used%20in%20your%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20base%20price%20for%20petrol%20is%20Rs%2057.07%20per%20litre%2C%20with%20an%20additional%200.20%20paisa%20added%20as%20freight%20charges%2C%20making%20the%20dealer%E2%80%99s%20cost%20to%20the%20oil%20company.%20The%20state%20imposes%20a%20uniform%20statewide%20tax%20of%2025.9%25%2C%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2021.17%20paisa.%20Furthermore%2C%20excise%20duty%20and%20road%20cess%20charged%20by%20the%20central%20government%20add%20up%20to%20Rs%2019.90%20per%20litre.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20commission%20paid%20to%20petrol%20pump%20dealers%20is%20Rs%203.84%20per%20litre.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20purchasing%20petrol%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%20101.94%20per%20litre%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20taxes%20and%20duties%20component%20amount%20to%20Rs%2044.67%20paisa.%20If%20a%20family%20uses%20around%2050%20litres%20of%20petrol%20in%20a%20month%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20GST%20paid%20for%20other%20purchases%2C%20they%20additionally%20pay%20Rs%202%2C233%20every%20month%20for%20vehicle%20fuel%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20of%20course%2C%20there%20is%20the%20property%20tax%20that%20you%20pay%20every%20year%2C%20stamp%20duty%20charges%20on%20important%20transactions.%20Service%20charges%20on%20all%20your%20loans%20are%20taxed%20at%2018%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20individuals%20also%20pay%20a%20health%20and%20education%20cess%20at%204%25%20on%20their%20income%20tax.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20there%20is%20the%20GST%20compensation%20cess%2C%20national%20calamity%20contingent%20duty%20on%20tobacco%20and%20tobacco%20products%2C%20building%20and%20other%20construction%20welfare%20cess%2C%20road%20and%20infrastructure%20cess%2C%20cess%20on%20crude%20oil%2C%20cess%20on%20exports%2C%20etc.%20that%20goes%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20not%20shared%20with%20the%20states.%20These%20taxes%20are%20levied%20on%20the%20tax%20liability%2C%20including%20surcharges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20individuals%20use%20expressways%20or%20highways%2C%20they%20pay%20toll%20tax.%20For%20economy%20class%20air%20tickets%2C%20one%20has%20to%20pay%205%25%20GST.%20For%20business%20class%20and%20international%20travel%2C%20it%20is%2012%25.%20When%20travelling%20by%20train%2C%20the%20GST%20on%20first%20class%20and%20AC%20compartment%20is%205%25.%20Rents%20on%20building%20properties%20for%20commercial%20purposes%20is%2018%25.%20When%20one%20takes%20a%20ride%20on%20Ola%20or%20Uber%20in%20India%2C%20GST%20is%20charged%20at%205%25.%20For%20services%20availed%20from%20food%20delivery%20platforms%2C%20such%20as%20Swiggy%20and%20Zomato%2C%205%25%20GST%20is%20charged.%20The%20cost%20of%20medicines%20includes%20an%20additional%2018%25%20on%20top%20of%20GST.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20your%20income%20slab%2C%20the%20income%20tax%20varies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5BUp%20to%20Rs%203%2C00%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20NIL%2F%20Rs%20300%2C000%20to%20Rs%206%2C00%2C000%20%E2%80%93%205%25%20on%20income%20which%20exceeds%20Rs%203%2C00%2C000%2F%20Rs%206%2C00%2C000%20to%20Rs%20900%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%2015%2C000%20%2B%2010%25%20on%20income%20more%20than%20Rs%206%2C00%2C000%2F%20Rs%209%2C00%2C000%20to%20Rs%2012%2C00%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%2045%2C000%20%2B%2015%25%20on%20income%20more%20than%20Rs%209%2C00%2C000%2F%20Rs%2012%2C00%2C000%20to%20Rs%2015%2C00%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%2090%2C000%20%2B%2020%25%20on%20income%20more%20than%20Rs%2012%2C00%2C000%2F%20Above%20Rs%2015%2C00%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%20150%2C000%20%2B%2030%25%20on%20income%20more%20than%20Rs%2015%2C00%2C000%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20businessperson%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20possible%20to%20allocate%20most%20of%20your%20personal%20expenditures%20as%20company%20expenses%20and%20offset%20all%20the%20GST%20amounts%20paid%20against%20your%20own%20liabilities.%20Depending%20on%20how%20crooked%20their%20chartered%20accountant%20is%2C%20the%20business%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20accounting%20books%20are%20written%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20minimises%20the%20amount%20of%20income%20tax%20owed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20salaried%20middle-class%20family%2C%20sorry%20my%20friend%2C%20bad%20luck.%20You%20have%20to%20pay%20all%20taxes%20with%20absolutely%20zero%20provision%20to%20pass%20it%20on%20anywhere%20else.%20Every%20single%20rupee%20that%20you%20pay%20as%20tax%2C%20cess%2C%20duty%2C%20surcharge%2C%20etc.%20goes%20to%20the%20government.%20Cheer%20up%2C%20you%20are%20precious%2C%20very%20very%20precious%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20strongly%20encourage%20you%20to%20do%20this%20exercise%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20three%20months%2C%20retain%20every%20single%20invoice%20for%20the%20goods%20and%20services%20that%20you%20consume.%20Total%20up%20the%20taxes%2C%20surcharges%2C%20cess%2C%20excise%20and%20customs%20duty%2C%20etc.%20that%20you%20pay%2C%20add%20the%20proportion%20of%20income%20tax%20and%20cess%2Fsurcharges%20for%20the%20three%20months%20in%20consideration%2C%20add%20the%20taxes%20and%20cess%20on%20fuel%2C%20restaurant%2C%20pubs%2C%20in%20everything%20that%20you%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20calculate%20the%20percentage%20amount%20that%20you%20shelve%20out%20to%20the%20government%20out%20of%20your%20total%20income%20in%20the%20same%20period.%20You%20might%20surprise%20yourself%20with%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20the%20same%20exercise%20in%20the%20same%20period%20every%20year.%20That%20will%20give%20you%20a%20good%20idea%20of%20how%20price%20rises%2C%20or%20inflation%2C%20are%20impacting%20you.%20And%20if%20your%20income%20has%20not%20correspondingly%20increased%20during%20the%20year%2C%20then%20you%E2%80%99ll%20know%20how%20much%20poorer%20you%20have%20become%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20done%20that%2C%20take%20a%20deep%20look%20into%20the%20government%20programmes%2C%20projects%20and%20expenditure.%20It%20is%20your%20money%20that%20they%20are%20using.%20Also%20remember%2C%20the%20money%20saved%20in%20your%20banks%20are%20often%20used%20to%20provide%20loans%20to%20industries%20and%20the%20business%20community%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20government%20policies.%20The%20fate%20of%20the%20money%20invested%20in%20equity%2C%20bonds%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20too%2C%20depends%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20economic%20and%20fiscal%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20the%20rupee%20is%20also%20influenced%20by%20the%20balance%20of%20exports%20and%20imports.%20India%E2%80%99s%20trade%20relationships%20with%20other%20countries%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20this%20regard.%20Furthermore%2C%20domestic%20policies%20affecting%20the%20income%20growth%20of%20individuals%20in%20the%20lower%20economic%20strata%20can%20impact%20government%20revenue%20growth%20and%20the%20reduction%20of%20subsidies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Koshy%20is%20a%20consultant%20in%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707472800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09142614%2Fimage-1818.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fever-wondered-about-your-value-to-the-government-take-a-look-at-your-tax-contributions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Do%20you%20notice%20the%20GST%20charges%20on%20your%20purchases%2C%20along%20with%20other%20taxes%20like%20tolls%2C%20fuel%20cess%2C%20duties%2C%20and%20excise%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fever-wondered-about-your-value-to-the-government-take-a-look-at-your-tax-contributions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chernobyl's%20mutant%20wolves%20