%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%2C%20the%20deputy%20chairman%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20and%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%20He%20also%20worked%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20Secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20oversaw%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20as%20finance%20minister%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Singh%20has%20been%20described%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Caccidental%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D%2C%20Karan%20Thapar%20had%20interviewed%20him%20in%201999%20for%20the%20BBC%2C%20terming%20him%20then%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20likely%20candidate%20to%20be%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7inVRiqL-RQ%3Fsi%3DSMVUNdBFoofITc7v%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707468804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09142140%2FMMS.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanmohan-singh-likely-retire-public-life-farewell-retiring-members%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20aide%20of%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20told%20the%20Hindustan%20Times%20that%20due%20to%20his%20ailing%20health%2C%20Singh's%20%E2%80%9Creturn%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20out%20of%20the%20question%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanmohan-singh-likely-retire-public-life-farewell-retiring-members%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Max%20Healthcare%20acquires%20Nagpur-based%20Alexis%20Hospital%20for%20Rs%20412%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707468013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%