0Passing%20Through%20Odisha%2C%20Generated%20Interest%20and%20Enthusiasm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09125441%2FGFy0HPSWQAAkcF9.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBhubaneswar%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThe%20political%20temperature%20in%20Odisha%20has%20shot%20up%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra%20that%20passed%20through%20parts%20of%20Sundergarh%20and%20Jharsuguda%20districts%20before%20entering%20Chhattisgarh%20on%20Thursday%20(February%208)%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(rally)%20that%20saw%20Rahul%20holding%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Rourkela%2C%20a%20politically%20sensitive%20area%20where%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20replaced%20Congress%20as%20the%20dominant%20political%20party%20sometime%20back%2C%20the%20Gandhi%20scion%20made%20scathing%20attacks%20on%20both%20BJD%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20accusing%20them%20of%20being%20hand-in-glove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Flive%2FH2TpjW69ZFk%3Fsi%3DtEHgJpwAuduh1K-v%26t%3D3733%5C%22%3EIn%20Jharsuguda%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0which%20was%20a%20Congress%20bastion%20till%202019%20when%20the%20local%20MLA%20and%20party%20strongman%20Naba%20Das%20switched%20loyalties%20to%20the%20BJD%2C%20Gandhi%20also%20targeted%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20accusing%20him%20of%20misleading%20people%20and%20fooling%20them%20about%20his%20caste%20status.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EIn%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20said%20in%20Parliament%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20the%20need%20for%20OBC%20representation%20because%20I%20am%20from%20the%20OBC%E2%80%99.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20not%20born%20an%20OBC.%20You%20all%20are%20being%20dangerously%20fooled.%E2%80%9D%20He%20went%20on%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eto%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CPM%20Modi%20was%20not%20born%20in%20the%20OBC%20category.%20He%20was%20born%20in%20a%20Teli%20caste%20which%20was%20a%20general%20caste%20and%20included%20in%20the%20OBC%20category%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%202000.%20He%20will%20never%20allow%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahul%20who%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20penchant%20for%20costly%20suits.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20never%20shakes%20hands%20with%20or%20hugs%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%2C%20Kisans%20or%20Mazdoors.%20He%20only%20hugs%20Adaniji%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahul.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Minister%20for%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%2C%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20spoke%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20caste%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5B%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%5D%20OBC%20status%20was%20recognized%20on%20Oct%2027%2C%201999%2C%20two%20years%20before%20he%20became%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Minister.%E2%80%9D%20The%20government%20issued%20a%20short%20note%2C%20as%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Modh%20Ghanchi%20caste%20(and%20the%20sub-group%20to%20which%20Modi%20belongs)%20stands%20included%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20government%E2%80%99s%20list%E2%80%A6%20of%20socially%20(and)%20educationally%20backward%20class%20and%20OBCs.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Frahul-gandhi-contests-prime-minister-narendra-modis-claim-of-being-of-obc-origin%2Fcid%2F1999253%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Frahul-gandhi-contests-prime-minister-narendra-modis-claim-of-being-of-obc-origin%2Fcid%2F1999253%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707546229273000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1m5poQQE1HRQ63YGODKdFO%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0quotes%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Egovernment%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Enote%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20survey%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Mandal%20Commission%20prepared%20a%20list%20of%20OBCs%20under%20Index%2091(A)%2C%20which%20included%20the%20Modh%20Ghanchi%20caste.%20The%20Indian%20Government%E2%80%99s%20list%20(of)%20105%20OBC%20castes%20for%20Gujarat%20has%20also%20included%20Modh%20Ghanchi.%E2%80%9D%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20note%20said%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20had%20included%20the%20Modh%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EGhanchi%20in%20the%20OBC%20list%20in%201994%20and%20the%20Centre%20in%202000.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Congress%20was%20in%20government%20in%20Gujarat%20in%201994%20and%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20centre%20in%202000.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20also%20did%20not%20spare%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20BJD%20government%20in%20the%20state%20for%20supporting%20the%20BJP%20inside%20the%20parliament.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20this%20happening%20in%20the%20parliament.%20Both%20the%20parties%20are%20in%20a%20partnership%20in%20Odisha.%20They%20are%20looting%20the%20lands%20of%20tribals%20and%20farmers%20and%20handing%20them%20to%20industrialists%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarked%20the%20Congress%20MP%20who%20was%20accorded%20a%20rousing%20reception%20as%20he%20arrived%20in%20Birmitrapur%20on%20February%206%20to%20lead%20the%20Odisha%20leg%20of%20the%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERousing%20response%20in%20Rourkela%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20mingled%20freely%20with%20the%20people%20in%20tribal-dominated%20Birmitrapur%20inquiring%20about%20their%20problems%20and%20promising%20solutions.%20His%20roadshow%20in%20Rourkela%20also%20evoked%20a%20great%20response%20with%20people%20rushing%20to%20touch%20his%20jeep%20and%20get%20as%20close%20to%20him%20as%20possible.%20It%20was%20clearly%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20party%20to%20revive%20its%20fortunes%20in%20Sundergarh%20district%20and%20its%20nearby%20areas%20where%20Congress%20once%20ruled%20the%20roost.%20The%20Sundargarh%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20represented%20by%20former%20union%20minister%20and%20BJP%20veteran%20Jual%20Oram%2C%20was%20won%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20Hemanda%20Biswal%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20face%20in%20the%20state%2C%20in%202009.%20The%20nearby%20Bargarh%20seat%20was%20also%20won%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20following%20a%20consistent%20decline%20in%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20the%20entire%20western%20Odisha%20is%20currently%20dominated%20by%20BJP%20and%20the%20BJD.%20While%20all%20the%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20region%20belong%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20majority%20of%20the%20assembly%20seats%20were%20won%20by%20BJD%20in%202019.%20The%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20been%20out%20of%20power%20in%20the%20state%20since%202000%2C%20put%20up%20one%20of%20its%20worst%20performances%20in%202019%20when%20it%20could%20win%20just%20nine%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20the%20lone%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20of%20Koraput.%20Plagued%20by%20internal%20dissensions%20the%20party%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20show%20in%20the%20elections.%20The%20state%20leadership%20is%20hopeful%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20yatra%20turning%20things%20in%20its%20favour%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CRahulji%20is%20a%20charismatic%20leader%20who%20loves%20to%20interact%20with%20people%20and%20sincerely%20tries%20to%20solve%20their%20problems.%20We%20are%20sure%20that%20popular%20mood%20in%20the%20state%20will%20turn%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20yatra%20which%20has%20generated%20tremendous%20response%20everywhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20state%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20and%20former%20MLA%20Dr.%20Lalatendu%20Mohaptara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20leaders%20of%20BJP%20and%20BJD%20do%20not%20share%20the%20optimism%20of%20Congress%20which%20they%20firmly%20believe%20is%20unlikely%20to%20witness%20a%20positive%20change%20in%20its%20fortunes%20anytime%20soon.%20%E2%80%9C%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20Yatra%20touched%20only%20parts%20of%20Sundergarh%20district%20and%20there%2C%20too%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20make%20any%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20people%20who%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20his%20lack%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20tribals.%20He%20comes%20from%20a%20privileged%20background%20%C2%A0and%20only%20pretends%20to%20be%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20common%20people.%20But%20this%20drama%20cannot%20fool%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20face%20Mohan%20Majhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJD%20general%20secretary%20Bijay%20Nayak%20was%20even%20more%20critical%20of%20Rahul%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Congress%20leadership.%20%E2%80%9C%20Congress%20party%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Odisha%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time.%20But%20they%20did%20nothing%20for%20the%20state.%20Their%20only%20contribution%20has%20been%20institutionalisation%20of%20corruption%20which%20weakened%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20finances.%20The%20bad%20policies%20of%20successive%20Congress%20governments%20pushed%20the%20state%20back%20by%20several%20years.%20How%20can%20Rahul%2C%20whose%20own%20party%20governments%20in%20some%20states%20have%20failed%20to%20inspire%20confidence%20among%20people%2C%20accuse%20the%20BJD%20of%20non-performance.%20Let%20him%20set%20his%20own%20house%20in%20order%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EYatra%20energy%20enough%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Shashi%20Kant%20Mishra%20believes%20that%20despite%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20yatra%20generating%20a%20positive%20response%20in%20the%20state%20it%20may%20not%20have%20much%20of%20an%20impact%20on%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20in%20Odisha.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20the%20yatra%20touched%20only%20a%20limited%20area%20of%20the%20state%20in%20Sundergarh%20and%20Jharsuguda.%20It%20would%20have%20made%20an%20impact%20had%20it%20covered%20a%20larger%20area.%20In%20the%20gatherings%20where%20he%20addressed%20people%20%C2%A0he%20appeared%20to%20be%20making%20pre-election%20speeches.%20People%20take%20such%20statements%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt.%20He%20no%20doubt%20succeeded%20in%20drawing%20crowds%20but%20one%20cannot%20be%20sure%20that%20the%20message%20he%20wanted%20to%20send%20across%20actually%20registered.%20If%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20really%20wants%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20yatra%20it%20should%20do%20some%20serious%20work%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20improve%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20organi%3Cspan%3Es%3C%2Fspan%3Eational%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20state%20Congress%20leadership%20agrees%20with%20this%20analysis%20even%20though%20no%20one%20from%20the%20party%20is%20willing%20to%20go%20on%20record%20for%20obvious%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9C%20The%20results%20of%20the%20last%20elections%20showed%20that%20we%20have%20conceded%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%20to%20both%20BJP%20and%20BJD%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20rise%20of%20BJP%20in%20Odisha%2C%20where%20it%20is%20now%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20can%20be%20directly%20attributed%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20fortunes%20of%20our%20party.%20Unless%20we%20work%20hard%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20we%20cannot%20hope%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20either%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20yatra%20or%20that%20of%20anything%20else%20that%20we%20think%20can%20work%20in%20our%20favour%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20Congress%20leader%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707464428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09125441%2FGFy0HPSWQAAkcF9.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-j