124559.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68124559.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex%20Civil%20Servants%20Express%20'Deep%20Disquiet'%20Over%20State's%20Involvement%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22185025%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.41.27-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20group%20of%20former%20civil%20servants%20belonging%20to%20the%20Constitutional%20Conduct%20Group%20have%20issued%20a%20statement%20expressing%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20disquiet%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20held%20on%20January%2022%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CReligion%20is%20a%20private%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20have%20said%2C%20and%20so%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20imperative%20for%20public%20officials%20to%20be%20mindful%20to%20carefully%20separate%20their%20religious%20beliefs%20and%20practices%20from%20their%20official%20duties%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2065%20signatories%20%E2%80%93%20from%20across%20the%20services%20%E2%80%93%20include%20A.S.%20Dulat%2C%20M.G.%20Devasahayam%2C%20K.%20Sujatha%20Rao%2C%20Rana%20Banerji%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20As%20a%20group%20of%20former%20civil%20servants%20deeply%20committed%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20its%20morality%2C%20we%20issue%20this%20open%20statement%20to%20express%20our%20deep%20disquiet%20about%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Indian%20state%20was%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%2022%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Religion%20is%20a%20private%20matter%20according%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20arrangements.%20All%20persons%2C%20including%20public%20officials%2C%20are%20free%20to%20follow%20their%20religious%20beliefs.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20for%20public%20officials%20to%20be%20mindful%20to%20carefully%20separate%20their%20religious%20beliefs%20and%20practices%20from%20their%20official%20duties.%20This%20is%20especially%20important%20for%20a%20person%20holding%20the%20high%20constitutional%20office%20of%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20as%20the%20leader%20not%20just%20of%20people%20of%20one%20religious%20identity%20but%20of%20all%20people%20of%20India%20of%20diverse%20religious%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20This%20separation%20between%20personal%20religious%20belief%20and%20practice%20and%20official%20duties%20was%20breached%20on%2022%20January%202024%20when%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20statue%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20was%20installed%20and%20consecrated%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20event%20brings%20to%20our%20mind%20the%20advice%20given%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20to%20President%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20reconstructed%20Somnath%20Temple%20in%20Gujarat%20at%20a%20juncture%20when%20the%20wounds%20of%20Partition%20were%20still%20healing%20in%20the%20subcontinent%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20not%20merely%20visiting%20a%20temple%2C%20which%20can%20certainly%20be%20done%20by%20you%20or%20anyone%20else%2C%20but%20rather%20participating%20in%20a%20significant%20function%20which%20unfortunately%20has%20some%20implications%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20In%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20idol%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20was%20undertaken%20at%20a%20site%20where%2C%20while%20granting%20the%20right%20to%20construct%20the%20temple%20at%20the%20site%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20clearly%20observed%20in%20its%20judgment%20of%209%20November%202019%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThe%20exclusion%20of%20the%20Muslims%20from%20worship%20and%20possession%20took%20place%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20between%2022%2F23%20December%201949%20when%20the%20mosque%20was%20desecrated%20by%20the%20installation%20of%20Hindu%20idols.%20The%20ouster%20of%20the%20Muslims%20on%20that%20occasion%20was%20not%20through%20any%20lawful%20authority%20but%20through%20an%20act%20which%20was%20calculated%20to%20deprive%20them%20of%20their%20place%20of%20worship.%20After%20the%20proceedings%20under%20Section%20145%20of%20CrPC%201898%20were%20initiated%20and%20a%20receiver%20was%20appointed%20following%20the%20attachment%20of%20the%20inner%20courtyard%2C%20worship%20of%20the%20Hindu%20idols%20was%20permitted.%20During%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20suits%2C%20the%20entire%20structure%20of%20the%20mosque%20was%20brought%20down%20in%20a%20calculated%20act%20of%20destroying%20a%20place%20of%20public%20worship.%20The%20Muslims%20have%20been%20wrongly%20deprived%20of%20a%20mosque%20which%20had%20been%20constructed%20well%20over%20450%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Despite%20its%20above%20observations%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20permitted%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20a%20trust%20set%20up%20under%20Section%206%20of%20the%20Acquisition%20of%20Certain%20Area%20at%20Ayodhya%20Act%201993.%20Given%20the%20troubled%20history%20of%20the%20last%20three%20decades%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20in%20the%20fitness%20of%20things%20if%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20temple%20had%20been%20undertaken%20by%20heads%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religious%20faith%20rather%20than%20by%20a%20constitutional%20functionary%2C%20which%20goes%20against%20the%20basic%20credo%20of%20secularism%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Preamble%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Of%20even%20greater%20concern%20to%20us%20are%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20last%20month%20before%20and%20after%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20temple.%20In%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20at%20Ayodhya%20on%2022%20January%202024%2C%20he%20affirmed%20that%20the%20Ram%20temple%20construction%20reflected%20Indian%20society%E2%80%99s%20maturity.%20Further%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20the%20consecration%20was%20an%20occasion%20of%20not%20merely%20triumph%20but%20humility%20too.%20However%2C%20the%20incidents%20at%20Mira%20Road%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20some%20other%20places%20in%20the%20country%20have%20witnessed%20a%20wholly%20unnecessary%20show%20of%20triumphalism%20by%20certain%20elements%20from%20the%20Hindu%20community%20leading%20to%20reactions%20from%20elements%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20At%20times%20like%20these%2C%20it%20behoves%20the%20majority%20community%20to%20show%20restraint%20and%20maintain%20dignity%2C%20especially%20when%20a%20fractious%20issue%20has%20finally%20reached%20resolution.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20efforts%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20to%20raise%20fresh%20issues%20concerning%20the%20religious%20faith%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20Gyan%20Vapi%20mosque%20at%20Varanasi%2C%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20at%20Mathura%2C%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Shah%20Jahan%20Urs%20at%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20and%20the%20Haji%20Malang%20dargah%20at%20Kalyan%20(Maharashtra)%20%E2%80%93%20are%20unnecessary%20irritants%20to%20social%20peace%20and%20harmony%20at%20a%20time%20when%20so%20many%20more%20important%20issues%20confront%20the%20nation.%20Nor%20have%20matters%20been%20helped%20by%20the%20unnecessary%20haste%20shown%20by%20the%20authorities%20in%20Delhi%20in%20demolishing%20the%20Mehrauli%20dargah%20and%20madarsa%20and%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Sunehri%20Bagh%20Masjid%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20New%20Delhi%20ostensibly%20on%20grounds%20of%20streamlining%20traffic%20flow.%20Surely%2C%20government%20agencies%20should%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20propriety%20to%20know%20when%20to%20bring%20up%20contentious%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20As%20a%20multicultural%20society%20which%20has%20absorbed%20people%20from%20so%20many%20other%20lands%20over%20millennia%2C%20it%20ill%20behoves%20us%20as%20a%20nation%20for%20its%20citizens%20to%20adopt%20a%20narrow%2C%20xenophobic%20approach%20towards%20those%20who%20have%20different%20religious%20beliefs%20or%20belong%20to%20other%20ethnic%20communities.%20India%E2%80%99s%20status%20in%20the%20world%20since%201947%20has%20been%2C%20to%20a%20considerable%20extent%2C%20founded%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20successfully%20run%20a%20country%20of%20so%20many%20diverse%20groups%20and%20faiths%20on%20democratic%20principles.%20It%20is%20the%20primary%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Union%20Government%20and%20the%20State%20Governments%20to%20maintain%20an%20equal%20distance%20from%20all%20religions%2C%20inculcate%20in%20their%20citizens%20the%20principle%20of%20fraternity%20enjoined%20by%20the%20Preamble%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20apply%20strictly%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20in%20ensuring%20that%20all%20citizens%20conduct%20their%20day%20to%20day%20affairs%20as%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20the%20laws%20thereunder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESATYAMEVA%20JAYATE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstitutional%20Conduct%20Group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0(65%20signatories%2C%20as%20below)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20width%3D%5C%22577%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2256%5C%22%3E1.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22111%5C%22%3EAnita%20Agnihotri%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2291%5C%22%3EIAS%20(Retd.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22318%5C%22%3EFormer%20Secretary%2C%20Department%20of%20Social%20Justice%20Empowerment%2C%20GoI%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2256%5C%22%3E2.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22111%5C%22%3EAnand%20Arni%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2291%5C%22%3ERAS%20(Retd.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22318%5C%22%3EFormer%20Special%20Secretary%2C%20Cabinet%20Secretar