aking%20time%20off%20following%20his%20wife%20Princess%20Kate's%20abdominal%20surgery.%20Prince%20Harry%2C%20who%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Meghan%20Markle%20abdicated%20their%20royal%20titles%20in%202020%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20is%20en%20route%20to%20London%2C%20having%20been%20informed%20of%20his%20father's%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20royal%20commentator%20Ian%20Pelham%20Turner%20shared%20exclusive%20insights%20with%20NDTV%20on%20how%20the%20royal%20family%20is%20functioning%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20said%20that%20he%20is%20at%20the%20moment%20able%20to%20continue%20looking%20at%20the%20red%20boxes%2C%20the%20official%20boxes%20that%20government%20departments%20send%20to%20him.%20It%20is%20thought%20that%20he%20is%20hoping%2C%20before%20too%20long%2C%20he%20will%20be%20back%20in%20public%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Turner%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fking-charles-diagnosed-with-cancer-says-buckingham-palace-5001016%5C%22%3EKing%20Charles%20Diagnosed%20With%20Cancer%2C%20Says%20Buckingham%20Palace%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20at%20the%20moment%20what%20would%20happen%20is%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20like%20Queen%20Camilla%20will%20start%20taking%20in%20some%20of%20the%20events%20scheduled%20for%20the%20King.%20The%20King%20will%20also%20have%20his%20audience%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20which%20he%20has%20every%20Wednesday.%20Queen%20Camilla%20has%20already%20taken%20up%20some%20of%20the%20royal%20duties%20that%20the%20King%20normally%20faces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20King%20Charles%20garnered%20praise%20for%20his%20candidness%20in%20discussing%20a%20prostate%20condition%2C%20prompting%20an%20increased%20awareness%20among%20the%20public%20about%20similar%20health%20issues.%3C%2