ds%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20one%20day%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20brand%20from%20scratch.%20Storytelling%2C%20to%20me%2C%20is%20powerful%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20share%20my%20story%20through%20a%20brand.%20I%20decided%20it%20should%20be%20in%20the%20consumer%20goods%20industry%2C%20even%20though%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20figured%20out%20the%20specifics%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20while%20studying%20at%20IIT%2C%20Ahana%E2%80%99s%20eating%20habits%20remained%20poor%20as%20she%20resorted%20to%20junk.%20She%20would%20fall%20sick%20often%2C%20be%20it%20at%20school%20or%20college%2C%20without%20realising%20that%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20was%20the%20food%20she%20consumed.%20It%20would%20be%20four%20years%20later%20at%20Harvard%20when%20she%20would%20come%20to%20the%20realisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%20does%20India%20lack%20healthy%20packaged%20food%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen6-1706874284.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Open%20Secret's%20factories%20are%20run%20by%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen6-1706874284.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen6-1706874284-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen6-1706874284-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen6-1706874284-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen6-1706874284-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen6-1706874284-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-imag