%2C000%20cookies%20later%2C%20Ahana%20was%20ready%20with%20the%20first%20product%20%E2%80%94%20the%20nutty%20cookie%2C%20which%20to%20date%20is%20their%20bestseller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20challenge%20was%20learning%20how%20to%20manufacture%20the%20product.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20product%20with%20no%20benchmark.%20I%20had%20to%20use%20my%20engineering%20skills%20to%20set%20up%20the%20right%20assembly%20line.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20work%20on%20extending%20the%20shelf%20life%20without%20adding%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20uses%20aluminium%20in%20the%20packaging%20to%20extend%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20her%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20finally%20launched%20%E2%80%98Open%20Secret%E2%80%99%20in%20January%202020%20through%20online%20and%20offline%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Open%20Secret%20has%20over%2030%20categories%20of%20products%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterin