es%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20communities%20on%20a%20global%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20universal%20nature%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20is%20pivotal%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20addressing%20the%20decline%20in%20SDG%20progress%20necessitates%20collective%20attention%20and%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnless%20we%20act%20now%2C%20the%202030%20Agenda%20will%20become%20an%20epitaph%20for%20a%20world%20that%20might%20have%20been%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAligning%20with%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%202030%20SDG%20Agenda%2C%20the%20NASSCOM%20Foundation%20recently%20organised%20the%20TechForGood%20India%20Conclave%202024%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Focused%20on%20the%20theme%20%E2%80%98Accelerating%20the%202030%20Agenda%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329369%2Ficse-2023-mobius-foundation-achieve-sustainable-development-goals-through-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainable%20Development%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20Technology%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20event%20brought%20together%20civil%20society%2C%20social%20innovators%2C%20entrepreneurs%2C%20government%20representatives%2C%20and%20technology%20and%20development%20leaders%20to%20collaborate%20on%20accelerating%20India%E2%80%99s%20SDG%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20covered%20essential%20topics%20such%20as%20sustainable%20living%2C%20climate%20action%2C%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20and%20empowering%20women%20entrepreneurs.%20The%20event%20included%20engaging%20masterclasses%2C%20fireside%20chats%2C%20and%20dynamic%20panel%20discussions%2C%20bringing%20together%20diverse%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20action%20today%2C%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20future.%20The%20TechForGood%20India%20Conclave%202024%20aims%20at%20uniting%20changemakers%20to%20accelerate%20India%E2%80%99s%20progress%20towards%20