holders%20is%20a%20significant%20obstacle%20to%20achieving%20SDGs.%20This%20hampers%20the%20sharing%20of%20best%20practices%2C%20innovative%20solutions%2C%20and%20lessons%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResource%20and%20competency%20gaps%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20recent%20NSSO%20survey%20highlights%20a%20digital%20skill%20gap%20among%20Indian%20youth%2C%20with%20only%2027.5%25%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%98digitally%20skilled%E2%80%99.%20This%20deficiency%20hampers%20the%20application%20of%20innovative%20solutions%20crucial%20for%20sustainable%20development.%20Furthermore%2C%20scarce%20competencies%20and%20resources%20impede%20the%20use%2C%20adoption%2C%20and%20creation%20of%20new%20knowledge%20and%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersistent%20Issues%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDespite%20significant%20progress%2C%20entrenched%20issues%20like%20gender%20inequality%2C%20the%20digital%20divide%2C%20poverty%2C%20and%20inadequate%20healthcare%20access%20remain%20substantial%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20these%20challenges%20is%20possible%20through%20the%20power%20of%20technology%2C%20which%20acts%20as%20a%20force%20multiplier%20and%20holds%20the%20potential%20for%20progress.%20In%20India%2C%20the%20digitalisation%20wave%20has%20led%20to%20a%20transformative%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20empowering%20individuals%2C%20improving%20data%20accessibility%2C%20and%20fostering%20inclusivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20next%20seven%20years%20being%20crucial%2C%20it%20is%20increasingly%20undeniable%20that%20technology%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20determining%20whether%20the%20UN%20SDGs%20are%20achieved.%20A%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20report%20suggests%20that%20existing%20technology%20applications%20could%20facilitate%20over%2070%25%20of%20the%20SDG%E2%80%99s%20136%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202452px)%20100vw%2C%202452px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett