igned%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20those%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329201%2Fgrailmaker-innovations-vision-nanny-platform-app-solution-for-kids-cortical-visual-impairment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20visual%20disabilities.%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20bringing%20this%20to%20fruition%20is%20a%20school%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20setting%20the%20bar%20high%20for%20its%20inclusive%20architectural%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20unique%20construction%20and%20thoughtful%20design%2C%20the%20school%20empowers%20children%20to%20rely%20on%20their%20other%20senses%20to%20navigate%20through%20the%20educational%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdorned%20with%20white%20walls%20and%20airy%20courtyards%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20Visually%20Impaired%E2%80%99%2C%20designed%20by%20SEALabs%2C%20is%20dedicated%20to%20these%20particular%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126863%2Fcan-help-visually-impaired-twitter-users-see-pictures-heres%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20visually%20impaired%20%3C%2Fa%3Echild%20has%20different%20needs%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20space%20that%20was%20inclusive%20of%20them%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anand%20Sonecha%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20SEALabs%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20this%20school%20help%20its%20children%20navigate%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20you%20asked!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Found%20inspiration%20in%20many%20place%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20started%20his%20practice%20back%20in%202015%20and%20had%20never%20worked%20on%20developing%20a%20school%20before.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Viren%20Joshi%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20school%2C%20a