3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20and%20running%20since%202021%2C%20Anand%20says%20looking%20back%20at%20his%20work%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20professional%2C%20I%20approach%20all%20projects%20with%20the%20same%20intensity.%20However%2C%20working%20on%20this%20project%20was%20unique.%20In%20our%20architectural%20education%2C%20we%20had%20never%20delved%20into%20questions%20about%20users%20to%20this%20extent.%20It%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20realisation%20that%20in%20designing%20any%20building%2C%20be%20it%20public%20structures%20or%20entire%20cities%2C%20we%20must%20consider%20a%20diverse%20set%20of%20users%2C%20ensuring%20that%20none%20are%20excluded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lesson%20of%20inclusivity%20that%20I%20learned%20from%20this%20experience%20has%20profoundly%20influenced%20my%20approach%20to%20new%20projects%2C%20where%20I%20strive%20to%20incorporate%20the%20valuable%20insights%20gained%20from%20the%20school%20project.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(All%20image%20credit%3A%20SEAlabs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706624472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Located%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20'School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20the%20Visually%20Impaired'%20is%20designed%20especially%20for%20children%20from%20remote%20villages%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20school's%20architecture%20incorporates%20the%20senses%20of%20smell%2C%20touch%2C%20hearing%2C%20and%20sight%20to%20help%20its%20pupils.%20Anand%20Sonecha%20of%20SEAlabs%2C%20the%20creative%20mind%20behind%20this%20distinctive%20design%2C%20elucidates%20the%20concept%20behind%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22