t%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Dhiraj%20Takri%20(%40dhirajtakri)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20gained%20about%2010%2C000%20followers%2C%20my%20brother%20ordered%20a%20phone%20and%20camera%20for%20me.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20phone%20and%20camera%20were%20delivered%20home%2C%20my%20follower%20count%20had%20risen%20to%20about%20300%2C000.%20I%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20learnt%20how%20to%20operate%20a%20camera.%20I%20use%20my%20phone%20to%20make%20all%20my%20videos%20(reels).%20It%20takes%20a%20little%20time%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20operate%20a%20camera%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20reels%20I%E2%80%99ve%20posted%20on%20IG%20have%20been%20shot%20in%20my%20village%20and%20on%20my%20Motorola%20Moto%20G40%20smartphone.%20However%2C%20in%20making%20these%20reels%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20broken%20the%20screen%20but%20decided%20to%20not%20change%20or%20replace%20it%20since%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20I%20will%20buy%20a%20new%20phone%20once%20I%20have%20the%20money%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20negativity%20%26amp%3B%20fame%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20when%20Dhiraj%20Takri%20started%20making%20reels%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20getting%20a%20single%20comment.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20first%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20he%20received%20many%20hateful%20and%20tasteless%20comments%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20also%20went%20on%20for%20only%20a%20week%20or%20two.%20Once%20my%20other%20videos%20started%20to%20go%20viral%2C%20even%20the%20negative%20comments%20trickled%20down.%20Even%20those%20who%20called%20me%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%20under%20the%20sun%20were%20now%20telling%20me%20%E2%80%98Why%20are%20you%20looking%20for%20negative%20comments%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhiraj%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20his%20family%20or%20fellow%20residents%20in%20Chitrakote%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20safe%20to%20suggest%20that%20no%20one%20expected%20his%20sudden%20rise%20in%20popularity%20on%20the%20internet.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20expect%20to%20grow%20at%20this%20rate%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20thankful%20to%20all%20my%20supporters%20who%20like%20and%20share%20my%20reels%20and%20follow%20me%20on%20Instagram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20my%20home%20is%20about%20one%20kilometre%20away%20from%20the%20village.%20About%20six%20or%20seven%20years%20back%2C%20our%20home%20was%20inside%20the%20village.%20To%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20my%20mother%20to%20travel%20and%20sell%20her%20wares%20in%20different%20villages%2C%20we%20set%20up%20our%20home%20a%20little%20away%20from%20the%20village.%20Since%20we%20lived%20a%20little%20away%20from%20the%20village%2C%20people%20didn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20know%20what%20was%20going%20on%20with%20me%20online.%20My%20friends%20knew%20that%20I%20make%20videos%20and%20that%20they%20have%20gone%20viral.%20Only%20when%20local%20TV%20news%20channels%20started%20featuring%20me%2C%20people%20in%20my%20village%20began%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopularity%20on%20Instagram%2C%20however%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20translated%20into%20any%20serious%20material%20benefits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20money%20on%20Instagram%20comes%20through%20partnerships%20with%20brands.%20Since%20my%20channel%20skyrocketed%20in%20just%20two%20or%20three%20weeks%2C%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20brand%20promotions%20and%20earned%20much.%20But%20brands%20have%20begun%20approaching%20me%20to%20make%20promotional%20videos.%20Things%20haven%E2%80%99t%20changed%20much%20for%20me%20%5Bmaterially%20speaking%5D%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20this%20is%20going%20to%20change%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20earning%20good%20money%20through%20his%20work%20online%20would%20be%20beneficial%20but%20the%20reason%20Dhiraj%20makes%20these%20reels%20is%20because%20he%20wants%20to%20develop%20his%20communication%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20as%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20teaching%20it%20%5Bconversational%20English%5D%20to%20people.%20Through%20this%2C%20you%20are%20not%20only%20helping%20people%20grow%20but%20also%20growing%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20longer%20videos%20but%20since%20people%20these%20days%20watch%20a%20lot%20of%20shorts%2C%20I%20thought%20making%20these%20reels%20was%20a%20way%20to%20earn%20a%20greater%20following.%20Since%20my%20content%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20people%20have%20been%20asking%20me%20to%20make%20longer%20videos%20on%20how%20to%20speak%20English.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20develop%20a%20course%20for%20people%20which%20will%20probably%20start%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(You%20can%20watch%20more%20of%20Dhiraj%20Takri%E2%80%99s%20content%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdhirajtakri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Instagram%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dhiraj%20Takri)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706622666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDhiraj-Takri-Instagram-1706621044.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhiraj%20Takri%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20content%20creator%20from%20rural%20Odisha%2C%20has%20become